<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package>
  <name>iri_poseslam</name>
  <version>0.0.0</version>
  <description>
    <p>
    This is the software associated with the following papers:
    </p>
    <p>
    V. Ila, J.M. Porta and J. Andrade-Cetto.<br />
    <b>Information-based compact Pose SLAM.</b><br />
    IEEE Transactions on Robotics, 26(1): 78-93, 2010.<br />
    http://www.iri.upc.edu/download/scidoc/1096
    </p>
    <p>
    V. Ila, J.M. Porta and J. Andrade-Cetto.<br />
    <b>Amortized constant time state estimation in Pose SLAM and hierarchical SLAM using a mixed Kalman-information filter.</b><br />
     Robotics and Autonomous Systems, 59(5): 310-318, 2011.<br />
     http://www.iri.upc.edu/download/scidoc/1226
    </p>
    <p>
    R. Valencia, M. Morta, J. Andrade-Cetto and J.M. Porta.<br />
    <b>Planning reliable paths with Pose SLAM.</b><br />
    IEEE Transactions on Robotics, 29(4): 1050-1059, 2013.<br />
    http://www.iri.upc.edu/download/scidoc/1419
    </p>
    <p>
    The Matlab code related to this package is in:<br />
    <a href="http://www.iri.upc.edu/people/porta/Soft/TRO-Doc/index.html">Matlab toolbox for PoseSLAM</a>
    or straight <a href="http://www.iri.upc.edu/people/porta/Soft/TRO-Code.tar.gz">code.tar.gz</a>
    </p>
    <p>
    These are the Spanish national projects that have made possible this software:<br />
    <a href="http://www.iri.upc.edu/project/show/83">PAU: Percepción y acción ante incertidum/bre</a><br />
    <a href="http://www.iri.upc.edu/project/show/115">PAU+: Perception and Action in Robotics Problems with Large State Spaces</a>
    </p>
  </description>

